title: Independent candidate Iftikhar Ullah Jan wins PK-64 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): The Independent candidate Iftikhar Ullah Jan has won the election for Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly constituency PK-64 Charsadda-III by securing 39,538 votes.
According to unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner up was Sultan Muhammad Khan of ANP who bagged 19,022 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 40.56 per cent.
